sentences.sentence: The polymer structure has the conjugated polymer backbone system having N-hexylpyridyl moieties.
sentences.translation: 聚合物结构是具有N-己基吡啶分支的共轭结构。

sentences.sentence: From thousands or more D-glucose moieties of sucrose the glucans, starch and cellulose, are built.

sentences.sentence: The anti-complementary activity of those polysaccharides seems that related to their whole moieties.
